public class StringLengthTest {

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        String a1="[{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >一、 前言</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >最近市面上一下子多了好多ITX机箱，这些机箱的各种设计都很棒，对于显卡、电源的兼容性都很出色，散热的表现也很不错。但其结构基本都差不多，没看到什么特别让人眼前一亮的ITX机箱。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >银欣在ITX机箱领域浸淫多年，其设计能力一直都是有目共睹的，也有很多设计十分出色的明星机箱产品。而前不久，银欣又推出了一个新款ITX机箱，SUGO14，这款ITX机箱的内部空间设计和其他品牌的都不相同，在内部空间结构上的设计非常大胆。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >你很难想象，在这种有限的空间内部，还能玩出这种结构设计。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"3\",\"content\":{\"img\":\"ceco/jfs/t1/148372/17/17686/66700/5fd034caEbf6a0660/981ea98cbad5ecb6.jpg\",\"threeCategory\":\"687\",\"twoCategory\":\"677\",\"title\":\"银欣（SilverStone）SG14 珍宝 ITX小机箱（高兼容/支持240水冷/长显卡/多存储）\",\"oneCategory\":\"670\",\"price\":\"499.00\",\"skuId\":\"100015037320\",\"imgList\":[\"ceco/jfs/t1/146216/10/6800/54854/5f4784f9E7f5873f4/bb41e5a9d0549afa.jpg\"]}},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >二、 银欣（SilverStone）SG14 珍宝\\n  ITX小机箱 开箱</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱的包装很小巧，正面印着机箱的型号和正面。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/148556/29/17516/129550/5fd029c3E23603472/c6f328e007d70e7a.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼侧面印着机箱的兼容参数，电源支持ATX，主板支持DTX。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/141029/20/17456/140552/5fd029d8E41f74a50/d49e378aad264369.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼包装内除了机箱之外，还有一些配件。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/150552/11/9821/155972/5fd029e2E3f81c6d9/96aa3a1ce52afebb.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >三、银欣（SilverStone）SG14 珍宝\\n  ITX小机箱 外观</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱的正面很简单，下半部分是透气网孔，左上角有银欣的LOGO。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/149454/13/17517/131267/5fd029eeEe430555c/a4d8d7a9f3dcb65f.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼右侧是机箱的IO面板，有三个USB接口，一个音频接口和一个重启键。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/154801/35/9171/124791/5fd029f6Ec11ca898/cda4f928aa9bd1b6.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱的正面很简单，只有一根竖着的黄线和一根横着的黑线，右下角还有一个开机键。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/145955/7/17686/93473/5fd02a01Ed0576e31/2f9f8ac4ea0d0876.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱的背面就是普通的金属背板，并无透气孔。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/149000/1/17555/85427/5fd02a0eE8ebee28c/840a0c1bd7ad7154.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱的尾部，可以大致看出机箱的内部结构设计。主板竖装，显卡横装。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/145238/16/17789/123404/5fd02a16E1af4a8ef/edba7375193d5e1a.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱顶部有透气网孔，内部依稀可以看到金属防尘网。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/131586/4/19046/150929/5fd02a1eEd807b649/3d60cde7c6c19bff.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱的底部也有透气网孔，内部也能看到防尘的金属网。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/135694/6/19121/137408/5fd02a26E3667e738/22effc865d6c2119.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼简单看了一下，发现机箱的四个面全部都可以拆掉，然后我就拆掉了，非常方便。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/151108/32/9767/181221/5fd02a2fE2dd0c500/98fd99ea7b9c587e.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼拆掉四面的金属挡板之后，机箱内部并不是一个简单的金属框架，而是各个部分都排列的很整齐。乍一看，蘑菇并没有看出来各个部分是安装什么硬件的，哈哈。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/129864/40/19156/130372/5fd02a37E2a80d50b/53f9ee135717efa2.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着蘑菇看看机箱的背面，也没看出什么名头。银欣这个机箱设计真的很有意思，让蘑菇一时摸不着头脑。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/144399/32/17651/120647/5fd02a41E4cf50bb7/949db66c38e0bab6.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼拆掉机箱正面的金属挡板后，蘑菇大概对机箱的结构有了一个大概的认识。左侧是主板位，右侧的中间是电源位，底部为显卡位。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/149244/24/17411/138846/5fd02a4aEb90d4ada/9ab4400beb3ce793.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼顶部还有一个金属框架，可以支持安装硬盘，亦或可以安装水冷，支持120、240规格。并且水冷排的安装孔位非常靠下，保证内存安装的兼容性。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/144063/14/17555/135023/5fd02a53E48aa683c/bf422f24ac03aafa.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着将机箱顶部的金属框架拆掉，可以看到，从这个角度看过去，机箱大概是一个框架。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/133947/36/19278/132093/5fd02a5dE14ccbb0c/6204f7ccf36d77da.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼机箱尾部银欣标配了一个机箱风扇，看样银欣是推荐搭建负压机箱风道的。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/141444/13/17614/132007/5fd02a66E86fcf79f/3f07ac89951c0110.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >四、 银欣（SilverStone）SG14 珍宝\\n  ITX小机箱 装机</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼这里搞一套小钢炮的配置，处理器是10850K，主板是技嘉的Z490I，散热是银欣的240水冷。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/155449/19/8951/141808/5fd02a7dE871af883/486ac9446925b9b3.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼主板的位置安装相对比较固定，就在左侧。240冷排的安装位置同样固定，在上侧。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/154280/21/9003/135652/5fd02a88E15705d90/5f918881f4a1e221.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着安装电源，安钛克的HCG850金牌全模组电源，这个电源的长度很短，仅有14cm左右，兼容性很棒。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/131031/8/19091/113148/5fd02a92E5a656e28/db98739180352061.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼规格120mm的散热风扇，在电源侧面占的面积很大，中间是安钛克的LOGO。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/154700/28/9083/140345/5fd02a9cE1651116d/fa728a7fa2c2618c.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼电源尾部除了开关和电饭煲插口之外，还有一个风扇模式选择按钮，可以在温控和静音两种模式之间切换电源风扇的运行模式。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/132501/25/18900/140711/5fd02aa4E4743aa4c/45cf305cd432d45b.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼电源的安装位置在中间，很有意思。电源延长线也是专门设计的，出线位在中间，兼容性不错。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/138576/24/17577/162810/5fd02ab0Ee021d86d/3b5528757c0eccfe.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着安装内存，扎达克的SPARK内存，8G*2，频率3600Mhz。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/150486/26/9781/100681/5fd02abaEec517f95/7e4acb0f96df9219.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼安装好之后的效果，水冷排靠前，内存的兼容性很棒。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/150722/13/9860/112711/5fd02ac6Ebaf60d2e/2dbcf3bb2c482eef.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着安装显卡，索泰的RTX3080天启，三风扇显卡，散热模组很给力。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/138586/24/17664/144952/5fd02ad4E490d99fe/2b2f47bc4e729a15.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼乍一看，这么长的显卡很难从机箱正面塞进去。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/135492/23/19091/155807/5fd02ae1E6e7e41a8/aaab52306a83301b.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼然后我们将机箱翻过来，可以从机箱的底部安装显卡。哎，其实这里也不一定是机箱的底部。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/131695/30/19031/148950/5fd02aeaEdbcb4289/52c82db3a2b5d731.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼另外，蘑菇注意到，机箱翻过来之后，底部还有一个显卡支架，设计的很出色，表面贴有橡胶垫，防滑、减震。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/142099/21/17632/173917/5fd02af6Edf14eab6/c1b9b60cc9e9b6d2.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼银欣这款SG14机箱的显卡兼容性不错，索泰这款RTX3080天启都可以轻松的塞进去。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/147662/13/17183/159480/5fd02b1dE5fbae171/cabdad37cf596a69.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼然后锁紧显卡支架，这个塑料的显卡支架是有卡口的，用力推进去，咔吧一声就能卡紧了。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/152372/30/9163/163254/5fd02b2aEb0e6cd27/b55005de0cb288d8.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼然后电源仓的背面还有橡胶垫，通过前后橡胶垫的搭配，让显卡牢牢的固定住，很不错。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/130293/35/19061/125784/5fd02b34Eaae1dcd3/3e5f93a0588eb2ed.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼安装好显卡之后的效果，机箱内部的空间还是非常紧凑的。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/149074/19/17577/137799/5fd02b40E7f8a8c30/51ae651c05724129.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼靠近看看，主板上部的空间还非常充足。如果不安装水冷排的话，风冷散热的高度兼容性应该也是一流。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/144950/19/17524/133698/5fd02b4fE1ffb5fa6/deaa5be770f0a252.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼最后盖上机箱所有的盖板，整机安装完成。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/142330/22/17543/137010/5fd02b58E6720c830/62b78ce71fdd8ba8.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼最后，在你想当底部的那个面贴上减震橡胶垫，整机就可以正常使用了。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/147013/14/17625/139858/5fd02b61E3bcfbadc/d389a89fb999d226.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼蘑菇选了一个较高的脚垫，垫起来之后感觉像是穿了高跟鞋，很不错。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/142486/16/17451/158619/5fd02b6bE04f382fc/d2fd0bd8cbad364a.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼开机，一次点亮，完美！蘑菇打开一下机箱的侧板，告诉你电脑正常点亮了。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/148214/4/17532/141895/5fd02b75E253de6c6/ad348e85e40b1f56.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼颜值还是很高的，银欣的这个水冷头很漂亮，灯效很梦幻。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/136626/32/19193/122207/5fd02b7eE4751e228/e91df20a59a1bd98.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼旁边是扎达克的SPARK内存，同样很漂亮。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/142905/36/17595/119480/5fd02b88E7ab9123b/9b5ae26face5eafe.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼底部的索泰RTX3080天启显卡的侧面灯效也很漂亮，有幻彩的ARGB灯效。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/130145/21/18990/132004/5fd02b91E1c4d7852/8837512ddca675d0.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼盖上机箱的侧面盖板，就不太能看到了。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/152605/15/9231/143162/5fd02b99Eab5eefb4/c2b9d72227194a93.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼不过，透过网孔，稍微还能看到一点灯效，很漂亮。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/152758/30/9129/135361/5fd02ba1E598fedd1/b86d32921c2778f0.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼整机效果，非常的小巧、精致。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x684_jfs/t1/144586/22/17750/119308/5fd02ba9Eba508a3d/034b3547f765a938.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >五、 银欣（SilverStone）SG14 珍宝\\n  ITX小机箱 评测</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼整机配置一览，10850K搭配RTX3080的配置，名副其实的小钢炮。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s980x600_jfs/t1/131181/33/19074/91506/5fd02bb4E4a7162c3/75129cc36c1857d2.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼简单跑个分，整机得分168W，处理器69W，显卡73.1W。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s980x600_jfs/t1/138986/13/17452/91428/5fd02bbdEf64e82d0/6e8e3c1effe61c03.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼ITX机箱，先测散热。室温22℃左右，日常待机，处理器温度36℃，显卡的温度在47℃左右，固态温度48℃，主板温度40℃，整体都还行。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1025x1022_jfs/t1/146326/6/17564/245722/5fd02bc7E256e3a76/a6cf7c7364daee4b.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼简单跑点CPU-Z的压力测试，模拟轻度满载的使用场景。处理器温度72℃，核心温度在71℃左右波动，整体散热效果不错。然后主板温度降到了38℃，显卡温度降到了44℃，固态温度降到了46℃。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1025x1026_jfs/t1/152266/20/9133/249568/5fd02bd0E55151231/4e71e304ef29dd2b.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着单烤FPU，处理器温度88℃，核心温度在85℃左右波动。显卡温度进一步降低，温度降到了40℃，很有意思。上部和后部出风，机箱底部和侧面进风，机箱内部的其他硬件温度都会降低，机箱的内部风道设计不错。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x1021_jfs/t1/131292/39/19059/255349/5fd02bd9E785b48b7/2d1356d7dadaa2f9.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼最后测试下显卡的散热效果，跑3Dmark的TSE模式的压力测试，帧数稳定率在98.1%左右。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x749_jfs/t1/152413/3/9110/149311/5fd02be2E5c1e51d9/81e2604429ca8ec2.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼显卡的核心温度在74℃左右波动，处理器的温度在45℃左右波动。可以明显的看到处理器的温度在缓慢的上升，显卡吹出的热风，被处理器的冷排吸进去了，些微提高了处理器的温度。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x748_jfs/t1/144010/39/17625/127510/5fd02beaEda54c7e0/72a2721c64f03d4e.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼处理器是10850K，10核心20线程，三级缓存20MB。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s397x400_jfs/t1/137985/32/17630/54200/5fd02bf2E80e8e765/2ddeca7111439f50.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼跑CPU-Z的压力测试，单核560.1、多核7003.6，性能强大。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s397x400_jfs/t1/143868/28/17683/39623/5fd02bfaEa82fdfe0/7ada836198759024.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼跑一下R23，单核1285、多核16097。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s612x918_jfs/t1/147267/11/17639/67852/5fd02c04E9e32cdc7/88d102fdb7dc6fb6.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼内存是双通道16G，频率3600MHz。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s397x400_jfs/t1/141698/2/17279/37660/5fd02c0eE6fe11837/5681765c5a110115.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼简单跑个读写测试，速度均能跑到50000MB/s，延迟48.9ns，性能强大。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s537x517_jfs/t1/136981/8/19127/64614/5fd02c16E31e9fac7/6d774729e652b062.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichTe";
        String a2="xt=true >▼固态是大华的C900系列，容量1TB。简单跑分2481，顺序读写1851MB/s、1751MB/s，4K性能方面，读取54.3MB/s、写入149.72MB/s。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s493x464_jfs/t1/139526/21/17514/54340/5fd02c1eEd72c0f41/5a3e6bf3e9495917.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼最后跑个3Dmark的FSE测试，下卡单独得分20673，性能强大。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1026x746_jfs/t1/139587/27/17781/139331/5fd02c27E9cb6624a/c95524b937062dcf.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >▼接着跑个TS测试，显卡单独得分17387。在2K分辨率下，这张RTX3080显卡非常强大，可以非常流畅的玩各种游戏。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true ></p>\"},{\"type\":\"2\",\"content\":\"ceco/s1025x748_jfs/t1/148042/6/17411/129089/5fd02c2eE6606a6e8/dee8469e7a35e8da.jpg\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >六、 总结</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >银欣的这款SG14机箱的设计也非常有意思，并不是那种将空间都空出来，让玩家自己选择的，而是通过合理的设计，将各种硬件安放在合适的位置。保证硬件兼容性的同时，还拥有出色的风道。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >并且在细节方面，可以看到银欣确实有自己的思考，还有一些特别有意思的设计。比如显卡支架设计，就会让显卡固定的很牢固，搭配上下的橡胶垫，可以将显卡固定的死死的。比如机箱四面无脚垫的设计，用户可以自己决定机箱的哪一面为地面，更加的灵活。比如电源延长线中置出线的设计，出色的电源兼容性，不会因为弯折而插不进去。这些都是很棒的设计，需要多年的机箱设计的积累。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >另外，这款机箱的风道设计真的很棒，主板前部还能再安装一把风扇朝外吹风，这样机箱就单纯从底部进风，打造一个负压机箱风道。</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >谢谢大家！</p>\"},{\"type\":\"1\",\"content\":\"<p class=\\\"richTextHtmlstr\\\"  isRichText=true >The End。</p>\"}]";

        String articleDescById = getArticleDescById(new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList(a1, a2,a1,a2)));
        System.out.println(articleDescById);

        String nul=null;
        System.out.println("zhe shi yige null"+nul);
//        System.out.println(nul.equals("1"));
        System.out.println(nul=="1");
    }
    public static String getArticleDescById(  List<String> descList) {

        if (null != descList && !descList.isEmpty()) {
            StringBuffer descs = new StringBuffer(1000);
            for (String oneDesc : descList) {
                descs.append(oneDesc);
            }
            return descs.toString();
        }else{
            return "";
        }
    }
}
